kÃ¶kÃ¼) bul + TRAIN/VAL/TEST ayarla\n# =========================\nfrom collections import deque\n\nIMAGE_SIZE = (224, 224)\nBATCH_SIZE = 32\nSEED = 42\n\nIMG_EXTS = (\".jpg\",\".jpeg\",\".png\",\".bmp\",\".gif\",\".JPG\",\".JPEG\",\".PNG\",\".BMP\",\".GIF\")\n\ndef has_images(p: Path) -> bool:\n    try:\n        for ext in IMG_EXTS:\n            if any(p.glob(f\"*{ext}\")):\n                return True\n        return False\n    except Exception:\n        return False\n\ndef safe_iterdirs(p: Path):\n    try:\n        return [x for x in p.iterdir() if x.is_dir()]\n    except Exception:\n        return []\n\ndef is_class_root(p: Path) -> bool:\n    if not p.exists(): return False\n    # p altÄ±ndaki alt klasÃ¶rlerin en az birinde gÃ¶rÃ¼ntÃ¼ olmalÄ±\n    return any(has_images(d) for d in safe_iterdirs(p))\n\ndef find_root(user_root: Path, max_depth=3):\n    # 1) DoÄŸrudan\n    if is_class_root(user_root):\n        return user_root\n    # 2) YaygÄ±n alt klasÃ¶rler\n    for name in [\"train\",\"Train\",\"dataset\",\"Dataset\",\"data\",\"Data\"]:\n        cand = user_root / name\n        if cand.exists() and is_class_root(cand):\n            return cand\n    # 3) BFS\n    q = deque([(user_root,0)])\n    visited = set()\n    while q:\n        cur, depth = q.popleft()\n        if depth > max_depth: \n            continue\n        if cur in visited: \n            continue\n        visited.add(cur)\n        if is_class_root(cur):\n            return cur\n        for d in safe_iterdirs(cur):\n            q.append((d, depth+1))\n    return None\n\nDATA_ROOT = find_root(USER_ROOT, max_depth=3)\nif DATA_ROOT is None:\n    raise FileNotFoundError(f\"GÃ¶rsellerin bulunduÄŸu sÄ±nÄ±f kÃ¶kÃ¼ bulunamadÄ±: {USER_ROOT}. \"\n                            \"LÃ¼tfen 'Add data' ile doÄŸru dataset'i eklediÄŸinizden ve gÃ¶rÃ¼ntÃ¼lerin alt klasÃ¶rlerde olduÄŸundan emin olun.\")\n\nprint(\"DATA_ROOT:\", DATA_ROOT)\n\n# TRAIN/VAL/TEST tespiti: DATA_ROOT genellikle train/ klasÃ¶rÃ¼nÃ¼n kendisi olur.\nTRAIN_DIR = DATA_ROOT\nVAL_DIR = None\nTEST_DIR = None\n\nparent = DATA_ROOT.parent\n# KardeÅŸ klasÃ¶rlerden val/test ara\nfor vname in [\"val\",\"validation\",\"valid\",\"Val\",\"Validation\"]:\n    pval = parent / vname\n    if pval.exists() and is_class_root(pval):\n        VAL_DIR = pval\n        break\nptest = parent / \"test\"\nif ptest.exists() and is_class_root(ptest):\n    TEST_DIR = ptest\n\nprint(\"TRAIN_DIR:\", TRAIN_DIR)\nprint(\"VAL_DIR  :\", VAL_DIR)\nprint(\"TEST_DIR :\", TEST_DIR)\n\n# KÃ¼Ã§Ã¼k bir aÄŸaÃ§ Ã¶nizlemesi (iki seviye)\nprint(\"\\nÃ–rnek aÄŸaÃ§ gÃ¶rÃ¼nÃ¼mÃ¼:\")\nfor d in safe_iterdirs(TRAIN_DIR)[:5]:\n    print(\" -\", d.name, \"(\", sum(1 for _ in \"dosya)\")\n","metadata":{"trusted":true,"jupyter":{"source_hidden":true},"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2025-09-24T11:20:32.888513Z","iopub.status.idle":"2025-09-24T11:20:32.889006Z","shell.execute_reply":"2025-09-24T11:20:32.888760Z"}},"outputs":[],"execution_count":null},{"id":"688ba13c","cell_type":"code","source":"\n# =========================\n# 3) TensorFlow/Keras Dataset'leri hazÄ±rla\n# =========================\nimport tensorflow as tf\n\ndef make_datasets(train_dir, val_dir=None, test_dir=None,\n                  image_size=(224,224), batch_size=32, seed=42):\n    if val_dir is None:\n        raw_train = tf.keras.preprocessing.image_dataset_from_directory(\n            train_dir, validation_split=0.2, subset=\"training\", seed=seed,\n            image_size=image_size, batch_size=batch_size, label_mode=\"categorical\"\n        )\n        raw_val = tf.keras.preprocessing.image_dataset_from_directory(\n            train_dir, validation_split=0.2, subset=\"validation\", seed=seed,\n            image_size=image_size, batch_size=batch_size, label_mode=\"categorical\"\n        )\n        raw_test = None if test_dir is None else tf.keras.preprocessing.image_dataset_from_directory(\n            test_dir, image_size=image_size, batch_size=batch_size, label_mode=\"categorical\", shuffle=False\n        )\n    else:\n        raw_train = tf.keras.preprocessing.image_dataset_from_directory(\n            train_dir, image_size=image_size, batch_size=batch_size, label_mode=\"categorical\"\n        )\n        raw_val = tf.keras.preprocessing.image_dataset_from_directory(\n            val_dir, image_size=image_size, batch_size=batch_size, label_mode=\"categorical\"\n        )\n        raw_test = None if test_dir is None else tf.keras.preprocessing.image_dataset_from_directory(\n            test_dir, image_size=image_size, batch_size=batch_size, label_mode=\"categorical\", shuffle=False\n        )\n    class_names = raw_train.class_names\n\n    AUTOTUNE = tf.data.AUTOTUNE\n    train_ds = raw_train.cache().shuffle(1024, seed=seed).prefetch(AUTOTUNE)\n    val_ds = raw_val.cache().prefetch(AUTOTUNE)\n    test_ds = raw_test.cache().prefetch(AUTOTUNE) if raw_test else None\n    return train_ds, val_ds, test_ds, class_names\n\ntrain_ds, val_ds, test_ds, class_names = make_datasets(TRAIN_DIR, VAL_DIR, TEST_DIR, IMAGE_SIZE, BATCH_SIZE, SEED)\nnum_classes = (Conv/Pool/Dropout/Dense) + EÄŸitim\n# =========================\nfrom tensorflow.keras import layers, models, callbacks, optimizers, regularizers\nimport tensorflow as tf\n\nfrom tensorflow.keras.preprocessing.image import ImageDataGenerator\n\ntrain_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(\n    rescale=1./255,\n    rotation_range=15,\n    width_shift_range=0.1,\n    height_shift_range=0.1,\n    zoom_range=0.2,\n    horizontal_flip=True\n)\n\nval_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(rescale=1./255)\n\ntrain_generator = train_datagen.flow_from_directory(\n    TRAIN_DIR, target_size=(224,224), batch_size=32, class_mode=\"categorical\"\n)\n\nval_generator = val_datagen.flow_from_directory(\n    VAL_DIR if VAL_DIR else TRAIN_DIR, \n    target_size=(224,224), batch_size=32, class_mode=\"categorical\"\n)\ndef build_cnn(input_shape=(224,224,3), num_classes=10, l2=1e-4, dropout_rate=0.4):\n    inputs = layers.Input(shape=input_shape)\n\n    x = layers.Conv2D(32, 3, padding=\"same\", activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(l2))(inputs)\n    x = layers.Conv2D(32, 3, padding=\"same\", activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(l2))(x)\n    x = layers.MaxPooling2D()(x)\n    x = layers.Dropout(0.25)(x)\n\n    x = layers.Conv2D(64, 3, padding=\"same\", activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(l2))(x)\n    x = layers.Conv2D(64, 3, padding=\"same\", activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(l2))(x)\n    x = layers.MaxPooling2D()(x)\n    x = layers.Dropout(0.3)(x)\n\n    x = layers.Conv2D(128, 3, padding=\"same\", activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(l2))(x)\n    x = layers.Conv2D(128, 3, padding=\"same\", activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(l2))(x)\n    x = layers.MaxPooling2D()(x)\n    x = layers.Dropout(0.35)(x)\n\n    x = layers.Flatten()(x)\n    x = layers.Dense(256, activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(l2))(x)\n    x = layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)(x)\n    outputs = layers.Dense(num_classes, activation=\"softmax\")(x)\n    model = models.Model(inputs, outputs, name=\"CarBrandCNN\")\n    return model\n\nmodel = build_cnn((224,224,3), num_classes, l2=1e-4, dropout_rate=0.4)\nmodel.compile(optimizer=optimizers.Adam(1e-3), loss=\"categorical_crossentropy\", metrics=[\"accuracy\"])\n\nckpt_path = \"/kaggle/working/best_cnn.h5\"\ncb = [\n    callbacks.EarlyStopping(monitor=\"val_accuracy\", patience=6, mode=\"max\", restore_best_weights=True),\n    callbacks.ModelCheckpoint(ckpt_path, monitor=\"val_accuracy\", mode=\"max\", save_best_only=True, verbose=1),\n]\n\nhistory = model.fit(train_generator, validation_data=val_generator, epochs=30, callbacks=cb, verbose=1)\nprint(\"En iyi model kaydedildi ->\", Path(\"/kaggle/input\")\n    all_datasets = sorted(os.listdir(INPUT_ROOT))\n    pick_idx = 0\n    for i, name in enumerate(all_datasets):\n        low = name.lower()\n        if \"car\" in low and (\"brand\" in low or \"class\" in low or \"logo\" in low):\n            pick_idx = i; break\n    USER_ROOT = INPUT_ROOT / all_datasets[pick_idx]\n\n    IMG_EXTS = (\".jpg\",\".jpeg\",\".png\",\".bmp\",\".gif\",\".JPG\",\".JPEG\",\".PNG\",\".BMP\",\".GIF\")\n    def has_images(p: Path) -> bool:\n        try:\n            for ext in IMG_EXTS:\n                if any(p.glob(f\"*{ext}\")): return True\n            return False\n        except: return False\n    def safe_iterdirs(p: Path):\n        try: return [x for x in p.iterdir() if x.is_dir()]\n        except: return []\n    def is_class_root(p: Path) -> bool:\n        return p.exists() and any(has_images(d) for d in safe_iterdirs(p))\n    def find_root(user_root: Path, max_depth=3):\n        if is_class_root(user_root): return user_root\n        for name in [\"train\",\"Train\",\"dataset\",\"Dataset\",\"data\",\"Data\"]:\n            cand = user_root / name\n            if cand.exists() and is_class_root(cand): return cand\n        q = deque([(user_root,0)]); visited=set()\n        while q:\n            cur, depth = q.popleft()\n            if depth>max_depth: continue\n            if cur in visited: continue\n            visited.add(cur)\n            if is_class_root(cur): return cur\n            for d in safe_iterdirs(cur): q.append((d, depth+1))\n        return None\n\n    DATA_ROOT = find_root(USER_ROOT, max_depth=3)\n    TRAIN_DIR = DATA_ROOT\n    VAL_DIR = None\n    parent = DATA_ROOT.parent\n    for vname in Ã¶ÄŸrenme\nloss = tf.keras.losses.CategoricalCrossentropy(label_smoothing=0.1)\n\nmodel.compile(optimizer=optimizers.Adam(1e-3), loss=loss, metrics=[\"accuracy\"])\nmodel.summary()\n\nckpt_path = adÄ±nÄ± bul\nlast_conv_name = None\nfor layer in reversed(model.layers):\n    if isinstance(layer, tf.keras.layers.Conv2D):\n        last_conv_name = layer.name; break\nprint(\"Son Conv2D katmanÄ±:\", last_conv_layer_name, pred_index=None):\n        grad_model = tf.keras.models.Model([model.inputs],\n                                           [model.get_layer(last_conv_layer_name).output, model.output])\n        with tf.GradientTape() as tape:\n            conv_outputs, predictions = grad_model(img_array, training=False)\n            if pred_index is None:\n                pred_index = tf.argmax(predictions[0])\n            class_channel = predictions[:, pred_index]\n        grads = tape.gradient(class_channel, conv_outputs)\n        pooled_grads = tf.reduce_mean(grads, axis=(0,1,2))\n        conv_outputs = conv_outputs[0]\n        heatmap = conv_outputs @ pooled_grads[..., tf.newaxis]\n        heatmap = tf.squeeze(heatmap)\n        heatmap = tf.maximum(heatmap, 0) / (tf.math.reduce_max(heatmap) + 1e-8)\n        return heatmap.numpy()\n\n    def colorize_and_blend(img, heatmap, alpha=0.45):\n        # img: 0-1 aralÄ±ÄŸÄ±nda (generator'den gelir), heatmap: 0-1\n        import matplotlib.cm as cm\n        heatmap_rgb = cm.get_cmap('jet')(heatmap)[..., :3]  # 0-1\n        overlay = (1 - alpha) * img + alpha * heatmap_rgb\n        return np.clip(overlay, 0, 1)\n\n boyutlandÄ±r\n        from skimage.transform import resize\n        heatmap_resized = resize(heatmap, (img.shape[0], img.shape[1]), mode='reflect', anti_aliasing=True)\n        overlay = colorize_and_blend(img, heatmap_resized, alpha=0.45)\n\n        plt.subplot(n_show, 2, 2*i+1); plt.imshow(img); plt.axis(\"off\"); plt.title(\"Orijinal\")\n        plt.subplot(n_show, 2, 2*i+2);     for name in [\"train\",\"Train\",\"dataset\",\"Dataset\",\"data\",\"Data\"]:\n            cand = root / name\n            if cand.exists() and is_class_root(cand): return cand\n        q = ===============================================\n# 5) Hiperparametre Optimizasyonu (Grid/Random Arama)\n# - Eski TF ile uyumlu (ImageDataGenerator)\n# - Auto-detect dataset\n# - SonuÃ§lar: /kaggle/working/hparam_results.csv\n# - En iyi model: /kaggle/working/best_hp_model.h5\n# ===============================================\nimport os, random, json, math, gc, time\nimport numpy as np\nimport tensorflow as tf\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom collections import deque\nfrom itertools import product\nfrom tensorflow.keras import layers, models, callbacks, optimizers, regularizers\nfrom tensorflow.keras.preprocessing.image import ImageDataGenerator\nfrom sklearn.metrics import classification_report\n\n# --- Reproducibility ---\nSEED = 42\nrandom.seed(SEED); np.random.seed(SEED); tf.random.set_seed(SEED)\n\n# --- 0) Dataset ve generator'lar yoksa hazÄ±rla (auto-detect) ---\ndef safe_exists(p): \n    try: return Path(p).exists()\n    except: return False\n\nneed_data_setup = not ('TRAIN_DIR' in globals() and hasattr(globals()['TRAIN_DIR'],'exists'))\n\nif need_data_setup:\n    INPUT_ROOT = Path(\"/kaggle/input\")\n    if not INPUT_ROOT.exists():\n        raise FileNotFoundError(\"/kaggle/input yok. Kaggle'da 'Add data' ile dataset ekleyin.\")\n    all_datasets = sorted(os.listdir(INPUT_ROOT))\n    if not all_datasets:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(\"/kaggle/input boÅŸ.\")\n    pick_idx = 0\n    for i, name in enumerate(all_datasets):\n        low = name.lower()\n        if \"car\" in low and (\"brand\" in low or \"class\" in low):\n            pick_idx = i; break\n    USER_ROOT = INPUT_ROOT / all_datasets[pick_idx]\n\n    IMG_EXTS = (\".jpg\",\".jpeg\",\".png\",\".bmp\",\".gif\",\".JPG\",\".JPEG\",\".PNG\",\".BMP\",\".GIF\")\n    def has_images(p: Path) -> bool:\n        try:\n            for ext in IMG_EXTS:\n                if any(p.glob(f\"*{ext}\")): return True\n            return False\n        except Exception:\n            return False\n    def safe_iterdirs(p: Path):\n        try: return [x for x in p.iterdir() if x.is_dir()]\n        except Exception: return []\n    def is_class_root(p: Path) -> bool:\n        return p.exists() and any(has_images(d) for d in safe_iterdirs(p))\n    def find_root(user_root: Path, max_depth=3):\n        if is_class_root(user_root): return user_root\n        for name in [\"train\",\"Train\",\"dataset\",\"Dataset\",\"data\",\"Data\"]:\n            cand = user_root / name\n            if cand.exists() and is_class_root(cand): return cand\n        q = deque([(user_root,0)]); visited=set()\n        while q:\n            cur, depth = q.popleft()\n            if depth>max_depth: continue\n            if cur in visited: continue\n            visited.add(cur)\n            if is_class_root(cur): return cur\n            for d in safe_iterdirs(cur): q.append((d, depth+1))\n        return None\n\n    DATA_ROOT = find_root(USER_ROOT, max_depth=3)\n    if DATA_ROOT is None:\n        raise FileNotFoundError(f\"GÃ¶rsel kÃ¶kÃ¼ bulunamadÄ±: {USER_ROOT}\")\n\n    TRAIN_DIR = DATA_ROOT\n    VAL_DIR = None\n    TEST_DIR = None\n    parent = DATA_ROOT.parent\n    for vname in [\"val\",\"validation\",\"valid\",\"Val\",\"Validation\"]:\n        pval = parent / vname\n        if pval.exists() and is_class_root(pval):\n            VAL_DIR = pval; break\n    ptest = parent / \"test\"\n    if ptest.exists() and is_class_root(ptest):\n        TEST_DIR = ptest\n\n# --- 1) YardÄ±mcÄ±lar: generator kurucu (batch size'e duyarlÄ±) ---\nIMAGE_SIZE = (224,224)\n\ndef make_generators(batch_size, seed=SEED):\n    if VAL_DIR is None or not Path(VAL_DIR).exists():\n        # train iÃ§inden split\n        train_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(\n            rescale=1./255,\n            rotation_range=15, width_shift_range=0.1, height_shift_range=0.1,\n            zoom_range=0.2, horizontal_flip=True,\n            validation_split=0.2\n        )\n        val_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(rescale=1./255, validation_split=0.2)\n        train_gen = train_datagen.flow_from_directory(\n            TRAIN_DIR, target_size=IMAGE_SIZE, batch_size=batch_size,\n            class_mode=\"categorical\", subset=\"training\", seed=seed, shuffle=True\n        )\n        val_gen = val_datagen.flow_from_directory(\n            TRAIN_DIR, target_size=IMAGE_SIZE, batch_size=batch_size,\n            class_mode=\"categorical\", subset=\"validation\", seed=seed, shuffle=False\n        )\n    else:\n        train_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(\n            rescale=1./255,\n            rotation_range=15, width_shift_range=0.1, height_shift_range=0.1,\n            zoom_range=0.2, horizontal_flip=True\n        )\n        val_datagen = ImageDataGenerator(rescale=1./255)\n        train_gen = train_datagen.flow_from_directory(\n            TRAIN_DIR, target_size=IMAGE_SIZE, batch_size=batch_size,\n            class_mode=\"categorical\", shuffle=True\n        )\n        val_gen = val_datagen.flow_from_directory(\n            VAL_DIR, target_size=IMAGE_SIZE, batch_size=batch_size,\n            class_mode=\"categorical\", shuffle=False\n        )\n    return train_gen, val_gen\n\n# --- 2) Model kurucu (parametrik) ---\ndef build_cnn(input_shape, num_classes, num_blocks=3, base_filters=32, kernel_size=3, \n              l2_reg=1e-4, dropout_rate=0.4, dense_units=256):\n    reg = regularizers.l2(l2_reg)\n    inputs = layers.Input(shape=input_shape)\n    x = inputs\n\n    # Conv bloklarÄ±\n    for b in range(num_blocks):\n        filters = base_filters * (2**b)  # 32,64,128 veya 64,128,256\n        x = layers.Conv2D(filters, kernel_size, padding=\"same\", activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=reg)(x)\n        x = layers.Conv2D(filters, kernel_size, padding=\"same\", activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=reg)(x)\n        x = layers.MaxPooling2D()(x)\n        # blok baÅŸÄ±na kademeli dropout\n        x = layers.Dropout(min(dropout_rate + 0.05*b, 0.6))(x)\n\n    x = layers.Flatten()(x)\n    x = layers.Dense(dense_units, activation=\"relu\", kernel_regularizer=reg)(x)\n    x = layers.Dropout(dropout_rate)(x)\n    outputs = layers.Dense(num_classes, activation=\"softmax\")(x)\n    return models.Model(inputs, outputs, name=\"CarBrandCNN_HP\")\n\ndef make_optimizer(name, lr):\n    name = name.lower()\n    if name == \"adam\":\n        return optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=lr)\n    if name == \"sgd\":\n        return optimizers.SGD(learning_rate=lr, momentum=0.9, nesterov=True)\n    if name == \"rmsprop\":\n        return optimizers.RMSprop(learning_rate=lr)\n    raise ValueError(f\"Bilinmeyen optimizer: {name}\")\n\n# --- 3) Arama uzayÄ± ---\nsearch_space = {\n    \"num_blocks\":   [2, 3],\n    \"base_filters\": [32, 64],\n    \"kernel_size\":  [3, 5],\n    \"dropout\":      [0.30, 0.40, 0.50],\n    \"dense_units\":  [128, 256, 512],\n    \"lr\":           [1e-3, 5e-4],\n    \"batch_size\":   [16, 32],\n    \"optimizer\":    [\"adam\", \"sgd\", \"rmsprop\"],\n}\n\n# Tam grid Ã§ok bÃ¼yÃ¼k olabilir; rastgele N deneme seÃ§elim\nall_combos = list(product(\n    search_space[\"num_blocks\"],\n    search_space[\"base_filters\"],\n    search_space[\"kernel_size\"],\n    search_space[\"dropout\"],\n    search_space[\"dense_units\"],\n    search_space[\"lr\"],\n    search_space[\"batch_size\"],\n    search_space[\"optimizer\"]\n))\nrandom.shuffle(all_combos)\n\nN_TRIALS = min(12, len(all_combos))  # hÄ±zlÄ± denemeler (istersen 20-30 yapabilirsin)\ntrials = all_combos[:N_TRIALS]\n\n# --- 4) Arama dÃ¶ngÃ¼sÃ¼ ---\nresults = []\nbest = {\"val_acc\": -1, \"cfg\": None, \"path\": None}\n\nfor t, (num_blocks, base_filters, kernel_size, dropout, dense_units, lr, batch_size, optname) in enumerate(trials, 1):\n    print(f\"\\n=== Trial {t}/{N_TRIALS} ===\")\n    cfg = {\n        \"num_blocks\": num_blocks,\n        \"base_filters\": base_filters,\n        \"kernel_size\": kernel_size,\n        \"dropout\": dropout,\n        \"dense_units\": dense_units,\n        \"lr\": lr,\n        \"batch_size\": batch_size,\n        \"optimizer\": optname\n    }\n    print(\"Config:\", cfg)\n\n    # generator'larÄ± batch size ile kur\n    train_gen, val_gen = make_generators(batch_size)\n    class_names = list(train_gen.class_indices.keys())\n    num_classes = len(class_names)\n\n    # model kur/derle\n    tf.keras.backend.clear_session()\n    model = build_cnn(input_shape=(IMAGE_SIZE[0], IMAGE_SIZE[1], 3),\n                      num_classes=num_classes,\n                      num_blocks=num_blocks, base_filters=base_filters,\n                      kernel_size=kernel_size, l2_reg=1e-4,\n                      dropout_rate=dropout, dense_units=dense_units)\n    model.compile(optimizer=make_optimizer(optname, lr),\n                  loss=\"categorical_crossentropy\",\n                  metrics=[\"accuracy\"])\n\n    # callback'ler: hÄ±zlÄ±ca en iyiye yakÄ±n sonuÃ§ almak iÃ§in patience kÃ¼Ã§Ã¼k\n    ckpt_path = f\"/kaggle/working/hp_trial_{t}.h5\"\n    cb = [\n        callbacks.EarlyStopping(monitor=\"val_accuracy\", patience=4, mode=\"max\", restore_best_weights=True, verbose=1),\n        callbacks.ModelCheckpoint(ckpt_path, monitor=\"val_accuracy\", mode=\"max\", save_best_only=True, verbose=1),\n    ]\n\n    # kÄ±sa eÄŸitim (istersen epochs=30'a Ã§Ä±kar)\n    history = model.fit(\n        train_gen,\n        validation_data=val_gen,\n        epochs=20,\n        callbacks=cb,\n        verbose=1\n    )\n\n    # En iyi val_accuracy\n    best_val_acc = max(history.history.get(\"val_accuracy\", [0.0]))\n    last_val_acc = history.history.get(\"val_accuracy\", [0.0])[-1]\n    last_train_acc = history.history.get(\"accuracy\", [0.0])[-1]\n\n    # val raporu (opsiyonel)\n    val_gen.reset()\n    y_true = val_gen.classes\n    y_pred = np.argmax(model.predict(val_gen, verbose=0), axis=1)\n    report = classification_report(y_true, y_pred, target_names=class_names, digits=4, zero_division=0)\n\n    results.append({\n        **cfg,\n        \"best_val_acc\": float(best_val_acc),\n        \"last_val_acc\": float(last_val_acc),\n        \"last_train_acc\": float(last_train_acc),\n        \"ckpt\": ckpt_path\n    })\n\n    print(\"\\nValidation report:\\n\", report)\n\n    # global en iyiyi gÃ¼ncelle\n    if best_val_acc > best[\"val_acc\"]:\n        best[\"val_acc\"] = float(best_val_acc)\n        best[\"cfg\"] = cfg\n        best[\"path\"] = ckpt_path\n\n    # bellek temizliÄŸi\n    del model, train_gen, val_gen, history, y_true, y_pred\n    gc.collect()\n\n# --- 5) SonuÃ§larÄ± kaydet ---\nimport pandas as pd\ndf = pd.DataFrame(results)\ndf = df.sort_values(\"best_val_acc\", ascending=False)\ncsv_path = \"/kaggle/working/hparam_results.csv\"\ndf.to_csv(csv_path, index=False)\nprint(\"\\n=== Hiperparametre SonuÃ§larÄ± ===\")\nprint(df.head(10))\nprint(f\"\\nKaydedildi -> {csv_path}\")\n\nif best[\"path\"] is not None:\n    # en iyi modeli tek bir isimle kopyala\n    import shutil\n    dst =
